e=\"line-height: inherit; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\">Each pack includes 3 coils.</font></span></p><p style=\"line-height: inherit; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0162/9487/1094/products/Vaporesso_PodStick_Replacement_Pods_-_CCELL_Packaging_1024x1024@2x.jpg?v=1593706973\" style=\"width: 500px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#000000\"><br></font></span></p></div>', '2021-07-10 07:41:58', '2021-07-10 07:41:58'),
(10, 'TFV8 Baby V2 Coils', '53', '/storage/product/4/UOQppneq0pXVvp1A9hyu.jpg', 'vaporesso_target_gtx_replacement_coils_-_0.2ohm_gtx_coil_blister_pack_and_box_1024x1024@2x.jpg', '<h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Graphik LC Web&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 16px;\"><font color=\"#000000\">SMOK TFV16 Lite 0.2 Ohm Coil Spec:</font></h2><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Graphik LC Web&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><li style=\"list-style: none; line-height: inherit;\"><font color=\"#000000\">0.2ohm Resistance</font></li><li style=\"list-style: none; line-height: inherit;\"><font color=\"#000000\">Conical Mesh Heating Element</font></li><li style=\"list-style: none; line-height: inherit;\"><font color=\"#000000\">60-85W&nbsp;Best recommended wattage</font></li></ul>', 4, 5, NULL, '100', '<h2 style=\"line-height: inherit; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; font-family: &quot;Graphik LC Web&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><font color=\"#000000\">SMOK TFV8 Baby V2 Coils&nbsp;<em style=\"line-height: inherit;\">Mesh</em>&nbsp;A1, A2 &amp; A3 (x3)</font></h2><p style=\"line-height: inherit; margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Graphik LC Web&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><font color=\"#000000\">The TFV8 Baby Coils V2 ‘A’ range are designed with a large heating area to offer fast heating capabilities, the range also come in three different colour options of stainless steel, gold and 7 colour.</font></p><h3 style=\"line-height: inherit; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Graphik LC Web&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><font color=\"#000000\">The TFV8 Baby Coils V2 ‘A’ range come in the following specs:</font></h3><ul style=\"line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Graphik LC Web&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><li style=\"line-height: inherit;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"line-height: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">A1 Single:</span>&nbsp;0.17ohm coil 90-140w (110-130w recommended)<br style=\"line-height: inherit;\">This coil comes with a large mesh centre, this system acelerates the heating process for a greater taste.<br style=\"line-height: inherit;\"><br style=\"line-height: inherit;\"></font></li><li style=\"line-height: inherit;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"line-height: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">A2 Dual:</span>&nbsp;0.2ohm coil 70-120w (85-105w recommended)<br style=\"line-height: inherit;\">This coil comes with two cobra mesh centres, this system accelerates the heating process and brings more airflow for bigger cloud production.<br style=\"line-height: inherit;\"><br style=\"line-height: inherit;\"></font></li><li style=\"line-height: inherit;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"line-height: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">A3 Triple:</span>&nbsp;0.15ohm coil 80-130w (100-120w recommended)<br style=\"line-height: inherit;\">This coil comes with triple mesh centres, this system accelerates the simultaneous heating process and brings even more airflow for bigger, thicker cloud.</font></li></ul><h2 style=\"line-height: inherit; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; font-family: &quot;Graphik LC Web&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><font color=\"#000000\">SMOK TFV8 Baby V2 Coils&nbsp;<em style=\"line-height: inherit;\">Wire</em>&nbsp;K1 &amp; K4 (x3)</font></h2><p style=\"line-height: inherit; margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Graphik LC Web&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><font color=\"#000000\">The TFV8 Baby Coils V2 ‘K’ range are designed to do everything from providing good airflow, trusty heating elements and great wicking capabilities to bigger and better clouds and flavor.</font></p><h3 style=\"line-height: inherit; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Graphik LC Web&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><font color=\"#000000\">The TFV8 Baby Coils V2 ‘K’ range come in the following specs:</font></h3><p style=\"line-height: inherit; margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Graphik LC Web&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"line-height: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">K1 Quadruple:</span>&nbsp;0.2ohm mesh coil 80-130w (90-120w recommended)<br style=\"line-height: inherit;\">This quadruple coil has four wire layers with a large airflow in the centre with excellent wicking designed for big clouds and great taste.<br style=\"line-height: inherit;\"><br style=\"line-height: inherit;\"><span style=\"line-height: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">K4 Octuple:</span>&nbsp;0.15ohm coil 50-110w (60-80w recommended)<br style=\"line-height: inherit;\">This octuple coil structure is made up of four holes, each containing two wire wraps bringing it up to eight in total with the intention to create more airflow and a rich flavor experience.</font></p><h2 style=\"line-height: inherit; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; font-family: &quot;Graphik LC Web&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><font color=\"#000000\">SMOK TFV8 Baby V2 Coils S1 &amp; S2 (x3)</font></h2><p style=\"line-height: inherit; margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Graphik LC Web&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><font color=\"#000000\">The TFV8 Baby Coils V2 ‘S’ range are designed for the Smok Stick series but can also be used with lower battery wattage devices.</font></p><h3 style=\"line-height: inherit; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Graphik LC Web&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><font color=\"#000000\">The TFV8 Baby Coils V2 ‘S’ range come in the following specs:</font></h3><ul style=\"line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Graphik LC Web&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><li style=\"line-height: inherit;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"line-height: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">S1 Single:</span>&nbsp;0.15ohm coil 40-80w (60-70w recommended)<br style=\"line-height: inherit;\">This single coil focuses on a low wattage but intense flavor and clouds with a longer life span.<br style=\"line-height: inherit;\"><br style=\"line-height: inherit;\"></font></li><li style=\"line-height: inherit;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"line-height: inherit; font-weight: 700;\">S2 Quadruple:</span>&nbsp;0.15ohm coil 30-70w (45-60w recommended)<br style=\"line-height: inherit;\">This quadruple coil focuses on a low wattage with intense flavor, a more restricted airflow but with big clouds and a longer life span due to direct wicking channels.</font></li><li style=\"line-height: inherit;\"><font color=\"#000000\"><br></font><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0162/9487/1094/products/head-coil-vaporesso-gtx-mesh-coil-06-ohm-500x500-0_1024x1024@2x.jpg?v=1595357052\" style=\"width: 500px;\"></li></ul>', '2021-07-10 07:45:36', '2021-07-10 07:45:36'),
