nt-weight: bolder;\">Pod Seating:</span>&nbsp;Magnetic</li><li style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; list-style: inside disc;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">E-Liquid Capacity:</span>&nbsp;1.3mL Refillable</li><li style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; list-style: inside disc;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Filling:</span>&nbsp;Silicone Side Fill</li><li style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; list-style: inside disc;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Contacts:</span>&nbsp;Gold-Plated Contacts</li><li style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; list-style: inside disc;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Available Colors:</span>&nbsp;Black, White, Blue &amp; Black, Grey</li><li style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; list-style: inside disc;\"><img src=\"https://provape.com/media/catalog/product/cache/896a704700b43f8a3d5d98936b485a9e/u/w/uwell-marsupod-pcc-kit_1.jpg\" style=\"width: 600px;\"></li></ul></div>', '2021-07-10 08:30:40', '2021-07-10 08:30:40');
